title: PSJ, SNPS, INTU, CDNS: Large Inflows Detected at ETF - Nasdaq.com
text: Looking today at week-over-week shares outstanding changes among the universe of ETFs covered at ETF Channel , one standout is the Invesco Dynamic Software ETF (Symbol: PSJ) where we have detected an approximate $154.9 million dollar inflow -- that's a 28.3% increase week over week in outstanding units (from 5,650,000 to 7,250,000). Among the largest underlying components of PSJ, in trading today Synopsys Inc (Symbol: SNPS) is up about 3%, Intuit Inc (Symbol: INTU) is up about 1.8%, and Cadence Design Systems Inc (Symbol: CDNS) is up by about 2.9%.
